      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This car is in absolute pristine condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior paint is flawless, showcasing a deep, mirror-like luster with no swirls, chips, or imperfections, further protected by a premium ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the high-grade leather remains supple and matte, free from any bolsters wear or creasing, and it still retains that distinct factory scent. Every technological feature, from the infotainment system to the climate control, operates with precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a rigorous adherence to scheduled maintenance using only OEM parts. This vehicle has never seen rain or snow and comes with a complete, organized binder of service history, original window sticker, and both sets of keys. It is a rare opportunity to own a piece of automotive excellence that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
